            <thetext>All values defined in the appearance &quot;client-document&quot; (like backgroundColor or color) have no impact at the application which is using this appearance.
The problem seems to be that the values are applied at the wrong time.

Current Workaround:
To solve this problem temporarily one has to move the values defined in the &quot;initial&quot; section to the &quot;states&quot; section of the appearance. When defined in this section the values are  applied correctly.</thetext>
